title: Men In Blue
content:encoded:
June 20, 2016 / Rabia interviews Michael Wood, ex-Marine and retired Baltimore police officer who became a nationally known figure when he began sharing some of the terrible things he witnessed in his 11 years on the streets of Baltimore.

Episode scoring music by Alex Fitch, AnimalWeapon, Blue Dot Sessions, Chris Zabriskie, Julian Sartorius, and Uncanny Valleys
